{
  "key": 18239,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_Yahoo",
      "en_US": "Yahoo!\r"
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_IGotSomethingCool",
      "en_US": [
        "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}: Hey, {STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}!\r",
        "I got something cool.\n",
        "I’ll show you as a special favor!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_CheckOutTheRuins",
      "en_US": [
        "Huh?\n",
        "What the...\r",
        "What’s this all about?\r",
        "...I got some Seals, but I forgot to\n",
        "put them on.\r",
        "Oh, right.\n",
        "It’s because I was at the ruins.\r",
        "The ruins here are cool.\n",
        "You have to check it out.\r",
        "Also the way to Celestic Town\n",
        "is blocked currently, so I’m\f",
        "heading to Pastoria City next.\r",
        "Anyway, I’ll battle you another time.\n",
        "See ya!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_BreathingInRefreshingAir",
      "en_US": [
        "Breathing in this refreshing air...\n",
        "It perks up Pokémon, don’t you think?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_TakeItEasySlowAndCasual",
      "en_US": [
        "Howdy, traveling Trainer.\n",
        "Take it easy, slow, and casual."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_TakeATourThroughTheRuins",
      "en_US": [
        "Howdy, traveling Trainer.\n",
        "There’s nothing here.\r",
        "Well, nothing but plenty of time to\n",
        "think, anyway.\r",
        "Oh, right. We have the ruins here.\n",
        "Why not take a tour through that?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_ImTooLittle",
      "en_US": [
        "I’m too little, so I don’t know\n",
        "how to battle very good.\r",
        "The nice Day-Care Lady is raising\n",
        "my Pokémon for me."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_EverySundayIVisitTheLostTower",
      "en_US": [
        "Every Sunday, I visit the Lost\n",
        "Tower..."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_OverTimeTheTownCameToBe",
      "en_US": [
        "There used to be nothing here but\n",
        "a road that went straight through.\r",
        "Over time, Pokémon and people just\n",
        "gathered, and the town came to be."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_IfYoureCompetentYoudHaveMetFiftyPokemon",
      "en_US": [
        "A traveling Trainer, huh?\r",
        "Tell me, how many kinds of Pokémon\n",
        "have you met so far?\r",
        "If you’re a competent Trainer, I’d\n",
        "think you’d’ve met at least fifty.\r",
        "If you haven’t, go farther abroad and\n",
        "search wider, youngster."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_ThisHeresAPoketchAppPokemonHistory",
      "en_US": [
        "Your encounters with Pokémon can\n",
        "be considered your shared history.\r",
        "This here’s a Pokétch app called\n",
        "Pokémon History.\r",
        "Use it to see your history of\n",
        "Pokémon catches.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_EachPokemonHasItsOwnHistory",
      "en_US": [
        "You have your history, and each\n",
        "Pokémon has its own history.\r",
        "When the two collide, new drama\n",
        "is born."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_MapSign",
      "en_US": [
        "Solaceon Town\n",
        "Free of Worry!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_SignPokemonDayCare",
      "en_US": [
        "Pokémon Day Care\n",
        "Let Us Raise Your Pokémon"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_SignPokemonNewsPress",
      "en_US": [
        "Pokémon News Press\n",
        "Wanted: Pro Pokémon Catcher!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_OnlookerCowgirl",
      "en_US": [
        "Yee-haw! Roll ’em, Whitney!\r",
        "That Miltank’s got more grit than\n",
        "any of the cattle back at the ranch!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_OnlookerHiker",
      "en_US": [
        "You made it just in time!\r",
        "Two Gym Leaders all the way from\n",
        "Johto, slugging it out up the route.\r",
        "Falkner’s the Flying type, Whitney’s\n",
        "the Normal type... what a clash!\r",
        "Whoop-there it goes again!\n",
        "Sorry, I can’t look away."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_OnlookerYoungster1",
      "en_US": [
        "I’m telling you, Whitney’s Miltank\n",
        "is gonna roll right over that bird!\r",
        "Rollout just keeps hitting harder\n",
        "and harder!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_OnlookerYoungster2",
      "en_US": [
        "No way, no way! Falkner’s Pidgeot\n",
        "is way too fast to get hit!\r",
        "One Roost and it’s good as new.\n",
        "You’ll see!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_OnlookerGuitarist",
      "en_US": [
        "The tension, the crowd, that big\n",
        "clash up there...\r",
        "This battle’s got a killer rhythm.\n",
        "I feel a new song coming on."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_OnlookerClown",
      "en_US": [
        "Heh heh! I’ll bet you a balloon\n",
        "Whitney bawls if she loses.\r",
        "She always turns on the waterworks!\r",
        "Ooh-nice hit! Where was I?\n",
        "Right, right back to the show!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTown_Text_OnlookerArtist",
      "en_US": [
        "Magnificent...\r",
        "The way that Pidgeot carves the\n",
        "sky, the power in Miltank’s charge.\r",
        "I simply must capture it on canvas.\r",
        "Forgive me, I cannot tear my eyes\n",
        "from such a masterpiece."
      ]
    }
  ]
}
